<section class=3D"differentiators">
  <div class=3D"differentiators-inner">
    <div class=3D"diff-header fade-up">
      <div class=3D"diff-label">The Embedded Operator Model</div>
      <h2 class=3D"diff-headline">This is not consulting. This is not coach=
ing. This is embedded leadership.</h2>
      <p class=3D"diff-sub">Four things make this model structurally differ=
ent from every other option you've considered.</p>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"diff-grid">
      <div class=3D"diff-card fade-up">
        <div class=3D"diff-num">01</div>
        <div class=3D"diff-title">Operators, not advisors.</div>
        <div class=3D"diff-body">Every senior operator in our network has P=
&amp;L responsibility in their background. They've made payroll on a Friday=
 when the account was short. They speak the language of real business, not =
MBA theory.</div>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"diff-card fade-up" style=3D"transition-delay: 0.1s;">
        <div class=3D"diff-num">02</div>
        <div class=3D"diff-title">Embedded, not external.</div>
        <div class=3D"diff-body">They're inside your business =E2=80=94 att=
ending meetings, learning the team, building systems. Not observing from a =
monthly call. They see what a consultant on a 2-hour call never will.</div>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"diff-card fade-up" style=3D"transition-delay: 0.15s;">
        <div class=3D"diff-num">03</div>
        <div class=3D"diff-title">Outcome-owned, not time-billed.</div>
        <div class=3D"diff-body">They own the result, not the clock. A coac=
h bills you for sessions regardless of outcomes. An embedded operator's rep=
utation =E2=80=94 and compensation =E2=80=94 is tied to your results.</div>
      </div>

      <div class=3D"diff-card fade-up" style=3D"transition-delay: 0.2s;">
        <div class=3D"diff-num">04</div>
        <div class=3D"diff-title">Invested, not detached.</div>
        <div class=3D"diff-body">We don't just advise your business =E2=80=
=94 we're invested in its success. We structure every engagement around sha=
red outcomes because we believe the best partnerships are built on aligned =
incentives, not billable hours. When you grow, we grow. That's the way it s=
hould work.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

