=94 built around your <em>stage.</em></h3>
      <p class=3D"cap-body">The gap between startup and scale-up is where c=
ompanies stall. You've outgrown the founder-does-everything model, but you'=
re not yet at the stage where a full-time executive team makes sense. That =
gap is where Executive District operates.</p>
      <p class=3D"cap-body">We embed fractional executives who integrate in=
to your business as if they're on your leadership team. They attend your me=
etings. They build the systems your team needs. They make the decisions you=
 shouldn't be making alone.</p>
      <p class=3D"cap-body">A fractional CFO who builds your financial visi=
bility and models your cash flow. A fractional COO who installs operational=
 accountability and removes bottlenecks. A fractional CMO who builds revenu=
e systems, not just campaigns.</p>
