e you're <em>ready.</em></h3>
      <p class=3D"cap-body">A successful exit isn't a moment. It's a proces=
s that starts long before the deal. Most founders wait until a buyer shows =
interest and then scramble to get their numbers clean, their team independe=
nt, and their operations documented. That's backwards.</p>
      <p class=3D"cap-body">Executive District builds exit readiness into t=
he fabric of how your company runs. We work alongside you to strengthen EBI=
TDA, formalize leadership structures, reduce owner dependency, and position=
 the business so that when it's time =E2=80=94 whether that's in 6 months o=
r 6 years =E2=80=94 you're not negotiating from weakness.</p>
      <p class=3D"cap-body">Our M&amp;A advisory and legal operations capab=
ilities mean we see the full picture: what buyers actually evaluate, how to=
 close valuation gaps, and how to protect your legacy through the transitio=
n.</p>
